name: IsItCorn
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: is it corn
des:
There comes a time in each person's life when he or she must grapple with the hard questions. Who am I? What is my purpose in life? Does any of it really matter?

This skill doesn't help with that.

This skill answers the question "Is it corn?" Simply ask Alexa, "is it corn?", and this skill will spit out a random answer, a vague response, or an inside joke to help you determine whether or not that mysterious plant in front of you is, in fact, Zea mays.

NOTE: If you can't already tell by the description, this skill doesn't actually identify anything, corn or otherwise. It just spits out random answers like a magic 8 ball, so don't come crying to me if it misidentifies your grains
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
